   Politics &amp; Policy:
   House Votes to Restrict Textile Imports,
   But Backing for Veto Override Is Weak
   ----
   By Peter Truell
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/19/90
</DATE>
